It was 1:30 when we rented the bikes.

00:04:22.180 --> 00:04:25.920
That explains why we were hungry. We normally eat at one o'clock.

00:04:26.320 --> 00:04:37.280
That's right. The lunch time in the office at our company is usually from one o'clock but now it's past two, so we will go back to eat because we are hungry.

